snippet.title: F-16 Fighting Falcon gameplay (PC Game, 1996)
snippet.description:
Gameplay for F-16 Fighting Falcon (aka iF 16), PC game produced by Digital Integration in 1996 - http://www.squakenet.com/download/f-16-fighting-falcon/5458/
Playing through a quick game scenario. Trying some dogfighting but ending in a crash due to bad controls of the jet.
Played through emulated Windows (Win 98/Win XP) virtual machine.
Recorded with original sound.

Similar videos you may like:
F-22 Lightning II - https://youtu.be/jcfeBaWoCR8
Dawn Patrol - https://youtu.be/2TvbdksBlas
